Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===MAIN===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然否定露娜 否定活下去 为何还要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有功夫分心啊 卡辛 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛 迪奥把卡辛带到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 林檎不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来治愈大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:41.80,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(576,390)}回归之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 这场战斗有了意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这瞬间 迪奥毫无疑问以战斗的形式活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 妈妈在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱妲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜的治愈又开始了 所以我逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎为什么和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我躲在那儿 她是被露娜的机械人扔到那儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人啊 在哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里毁灭的味道太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛 我一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易给你了永生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却一股死的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只会带来死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是渴求生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡与毁灭是丑陋的 这里不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想被赐予新生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 她可是想杀你之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥说 想拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥不是和你战斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了你 这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 是迪奥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丑陋 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛 你也清楚毁灭的丑陋和死亡的愚蠢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你那般洋溢着生命的人 只应和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才正是真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这建立起永恒的国度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有且只有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以永远生存下去 这有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 生命是有却没人活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像泉水一样洋溢着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是从其中取水而饮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 迪奥 和我遇到过的那些机械人和人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就像是燃烧着一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧总有一天会燃灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才觉得美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不死之身的我说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点说服力都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的不死换来的 是不能活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===INSERT===
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:40.69,INSERT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(200,400)\blur3}How long will it take to find a way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:47.51,INSERT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(200,400)\blur3}But she never lost the way and made herself to home
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:54.23,INSERT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(200,400)\blur3}So we hold each other's hand as we walk along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.34,INSERT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(200,400)\blur3}No matter fears and tears to fall
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:01.63,INSERT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(200,400)\blur3}We find a way of home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里找不到战斗的意义 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我从你身上也找寻不出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 来杀我的你是那么的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我心中的死都流向了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且将我从死亡中解脱 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道事情会变成这样 我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那时候的我 即使知道了也会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你解脱了 我或许会有后悔之心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副将自己说成是罪人的口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想夺取任何人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活着 为了燃烧生命而活 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容就是我活着的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远在一起吧 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 永别了卡辛 我会等待新的王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救莱妲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱金格·保斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了结束毁灭而来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借你的治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了 布莱金格·保斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来建造永恒的国度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再建立起机械人帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===ED2===
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:22:01.13,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\blur3\1c&H8F8F8F&}もうずっと君とは会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:07.36,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\blur3\1c&H8F8F8F&\t(0,1300,\1c&FF8000&)}僕はさよならもしまった
